text: 6-11-2019. I love this Mod pizza, the location is immaculate. The service was very fast.  All the team members I interacted with were very nice and helpful.  The build your own pizza I ordered was fantastic!!!!!  Parking is limited, but otherwise this location is fantastic!

text: I had a great experience at this MOD location. The staff were friendly and outgoing. My Lucy Sunshine pizza was delicious and arrived quickly. Store was clean and front garage style window was open so you could enjoy the day and feel the fresh air. I'd return and recommend.
